response.overview: Award-winning Aussie oddball, Josh Glanc, doles out original songs, tender crowd-work, and a wackily inventive absurdism all his own. Nominated for the Edinburgh Comedy Award and listed by Rolling Stone Magazine as one of the stand-out shows of the Edinburgh Fringe. Don't miss it. Or do. I don’t really mind. I’m just the guy who writes his copy. In fact I’m going to write whatever I want. Lalablahabal yimsdfi yimmo yoooo. Bing bong baaahh.
response.title: Josh Glanc: Family Man
